    Introduction


        Org\Heigl\Geo is a package to parse coordinates 
        and create graphical representations from them.



        I mainly created the package in the first place to read a file I obtained
        from OpenStreetmap.org and create an SVG-file from it.


        Theory of operation

Yes, there is one ;-)


